## Testing State Changes

```ruby
test "article can transition from draft to published" do
  article = articles(:draft)
  
  assert article.may_publish?
  article.publish!
  
  assert_equal 'published', article.status
end

test "published article cannot be deleted" do
  article = articles(:published)
  
  assert_not article.may_delete?
  assert_raises(StateMachineError) { article.delete! }
end
```

